summary: WHILE DRIVING AIR BAG LIGHT ILLUMINATED TWICE FOR ABOUT A MINUTE.  VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO AN INDEPENDENT MECHANIC SHOP. MECHANIC  STATED THEAT VEHICLE WAS UNDER  RECALL 00V105000  FOR  AIR BAG CONTROL MODULE.  THE VEHICLE WAS TAKEN TO THE DEALER, WHO INDICATED THAT VEHICLE HAD ALREADY RECALL REPAIRS PERFORMED, BUT THERE  WERE NO RECORDS OF  RECALL REPAIRS.   AIR BAG CONTROL MODULE MUST BE REPLACED AT THE OWNER'S EXPENSE.
